          "_name": "content4",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section content4\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-8\">\n                <h2 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"align-center pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">ANIMATED SHORT FILM &nbsp;</h2>\n                <h3 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">SAMURAI FROG GOLF - Directed by Brent Forrest, Japan\n<div>THE BLIND WRITER - Directed by Georges Sifianos, Greece\n</div><div>LOUIS I. KING OF THE SHEEP - Directed by Markus Wulf, Germany\n</div><div>BALL - Directed by Oday kahdum, Iraq\n</div><div>IDENTITY - Directed by Alireza Salehi, Iran\n</div><div>THE BASILISK - Directed by Chloé Delestrain, Owen Masson, Lancelot Myja Le Guludec, Morrigane Haudry, Nathan Peyren, Gaël Lejeune, Baptiste Belperin, France\n</div><div>YALLAH! - Directed by Nayla Nassar, Edouard Pitula, Renaud de Saint Albin, Cécile Adant, Anaïs Sassatelli, Candice Behague, France\n</div><div>PIR'HEART - Directed by Alicia Abdoulazize, Manon Desarnaud, Ida Thisted Jorgensen, Johanne Koffi, Robin Isola, Nikhil Gawankar, France\n</div><div>FROM ABOVE - Directed by Julien Jousse, Arthur Damiano, Vincent Hébrard, Léonard Haug, Antoine Thiaucourt, Hector Dao, Nathan Baussois, France\n</div><div>BOREALIS - Directed by Antoine M.Des Gavroches / Solène Juignet / Julien Giard / Noëlie Girard / Julien Tassan / Yann Meessen, France\n</div><div>GOLDEN COW MOUNTAIN - Directed by Yifu Feng, Japan\n</div><div>THE KISS - Directed by Ali Zare Ghanatnowi, France\n</div><div>FLEDGE - Directed by Hani Dombe , Tom Kouris, Israel\n</div><div>ILLUMINATED - Directed by Morana Marija Vulić, Croatia\n</div><div>OBJECT OF LIFE - Directed by Jack James Parry, Australia\n</div><div>REFLECTION - Directed by Alan Bidard, Martinique\n</div><div>A FLEETING MOMENT - Directed by Allyanna Demafeliz, United States\n</div><div>DREAM - Directed by Hoang Nguyen, Giang Hoang, Viet Nam\n</div><div><br></div></h3>\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-center py-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\">LEARN MORE</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\">LIVE DEMO</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "content4-1g",
          "_isUserblock": true,
